Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.28,0:41:00.95,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Right, the erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.02,0:41:03.32,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,The inflatable person has split. There's--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.52,0:41:05.22,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.29,0:41:06.69,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Mine's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.19,0:41:11.13,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Let's move on, shall we? Tonight we are in Morocco,
