Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.24,0:41:24.21,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the ape turned up, uninvited,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.28,0:41:26.98,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,in a ridiculously expensive Alfa Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.05,0:41:28.58,字幕ENG,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did.
